			Company Description 


			Siam City Cement Public Co. Ltd. engages in the manufacture and trade of cement. It operates through the following segments: Cement; Concrete and Aggregate; and Others. The Cement segment produces and distributes cement products, handles industrial waste disposal, electricity generation from waste h...
		


                Siam City Cement Public Co. Ltd. engages in the manufacture and trade of cement. It operates through the following segments: Cement; Concrete and Aggregate; and Others. The Cement segment produces and distributes cement products, handles industrial waste disposal, electricity generation from waste heat, and fuel and raw material trading. The Concrete and Aggregate segment manufactures and sells mortars, light-weigh concrete, and ready-mixed concrete products. The Others segment produces and trades wood replacement materials as well as provides information technology management and development service business. The company was founded on May 16, 1969 and is headquartered in Bangkok, Thailand
            




