STEPS TO APPLY FOR JOB OPPORTUNITIES



STEP 1




Enter our HR Area. Click the link below to Start your application process

ENTER TO APPLY HERE




STEP 2




Click “Sign In” or “Apply” to Log in. If you don’t have a Log In account, click “Create an Account” to apply for our job opportunities




STEP 3




After logging in, use the search fields to find available positions applicable to you




STEP 4




Complete the application form for the position that you are applying for

 







DEVELOPMENT   @INSEE  






DEVELOPMENT   @INSEE  


“SCCC has a strong passion in modern people development approaches focusing on the learners’ needs by experience/sharing, best practices, on the job coaching, classroom and self-learning, and encouraging continuous learning anywhere and anytime via self-learning, digital learning under the corporate knowledge management system, or Knowledge Management.”





WORK   @INSEE  



We encourage all employees to improve their effectiveness that would create true understanding of job responsibility which leads to the achievement of both individual and team success.

Working environment at SCCC promote good work relationship in all aspects. We treat each other the way we want to be treated and we believe that people work best when there is a foundation of trust. We encourage two-way communication throughout the organization and provide our employees good opportunity in their career paths.





